node.text:
3개월 동안 함께 해주신 모든분께 감사를 드리며 이 영상을 바칩니다. We dedicate this video to all the people who has been with us for the past 3 months and all the persons concerned with the Lotte Museum of Art. Thank you again. ‘THE OTHER SIDE’ at Lotte Museum of Art, 16th of April - 11th of July, 2021. @lottemuseum 

Music by_ @juniorchefmusic 
Directed by_ @liampark7 
Produced by_ @hyunjin_photo
